                    <span>Having meditated for over 30 years and having digested many books and teachings, I must say that the venerable monk has really done a great job!  This book is for the novice and for the long term practictioner.  I was delightfully humbled and learned as much as I have ever learned about meditation.  HOwever, please don't read this quickly.......digest it, read a few pages every day or so, and practice!  You will find a wonderful combination of great fun and serious self-work.</span>
                  
